p or incident boundary.","created_at":"2026-03-22T01:28:14Z"},{"id":350,"issue_id":"bd-j9jo3.1.5","author":"ubuntu","text":"Sensitivity follow-up: the normative example corpus must now include visible, preview_only, redacted, withheld, and hashed-evidence scenarios across snapshot, digest, attention, inspect, streaming, and replay so disclosure behavior is just as concrete as freshness or boundedness behavior.","created_at":"2026-03-22T01:37:20Z"}]}
